{% block body %}

  {{ form_start(form, {'attr': {'class': 'form-container'}}) }}

    {# Titre #}
    {{ form_row(form.title, {
      'attr': {
        'class': 'form-control',
        'placeholder': 'Place title here'
      }
    }) }}

    {# Date de lancement #}
    {{ form_row(form.launchDate, {
      'attr': {
        'class': 'form-control'
      }
    }) }}

    {# Image #}
    {{ form_row(form.imageFile, {
      'attr': {
        'class': 'form-control'
      }
    }) }}

    {# Description #}
    {{ form_row(form.description, {
      'attr': {
        'class': 'form-control content-field',
        'placeholder': 'Describe the mission here',
        'rows': 10
      }
    }) }}

    {# Agence spatiale #}
    {{ form_row(form.agency, {
      'attr': {
        'class': 'form-control',
        'placeholder': 'e.g. NASA, ESA'
      }
    }) }}

    <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">
      Save
    </button>

  {{ form_end(form) }}
{% endblock %}
